If &quot;A&quot;&quot;1&quot;, &quot;A&quot;&quot;2&quot;, &quot;A&quot;&quot;3&quot; and &quot;A&quot;&quot;4&quot; denote the area of each faces, the value of &quot;r&quot; is given by

